*******************************************************************************
t3sandbox (typo3 4.5.11)
*******************************************************************************

A blank typo3 project for install and play without wasting time setting up basic things as templates, base typoscript, ...


===============================================================================
Installation
===============================================================================

- Clone this to your server
- Add files index.php, typo3, t3lib (create symlinks to a typo3 4.5.x or download the "Source" from http://typo3.org/download/packages/).Typo3 core are not included.
- Import database db/t3sandbox_master.sql and modify mysql connection in typo3conf/localconf.php 
- change baseurl in fileadmin/templates/ts/page.ts
- change file permissions


===============================================================================
Libraries included in the project
===============================================================================
- Framework CSS Twitter Bootstrap 2.0.1
- jQuery 1.7.1


===============================================================================
Templavoila areas
===============================================================================
- Header (lib.field_header)
- Menu (lib.menu)
- Left menu (lib.submenu)
- Left column under left menu (lib.leftBlock)
- Content
- Footer (lib.footer)






